reviewText: Not as good as the fist movie, but definitely worth a watch. The two bumbling criminals are back for closure after repeatedly having nightmares of Samson and Hercules, this ambition leads the pair into a round of hilarious situations that the whole family will enjoy.
I am not kidding, I am in this movie.. It was filmed on my Navy vessel.. How Awesome Is That! My kids love it, cuz daddy is in it..
